# Git Ignore Rules
#
#   Excludes build artifacts, secrets, wallet sqlite data, and frontend node_modules
#   from version control.
#
# INPUT:
#   - None; consumed by git
#
# OUTPUT:
#   - Ignored paths for target/, .env, /data, node_modules/, web/dist/
#
# NOTES:
#   .env.example is explicitly allowed (!.env.example). Seed files never committed.
#
# Written by Composer for Ze Supply Chain. June 2025. All rights reserved.

# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Secrets — never commit the wallet seed; it controls real ZEC
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.seed

# Wallet + runtime data (rebuildable from seed + chain)
/data
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm

# Frontend
node_modules/
web/dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# Agents
documentation_agent.md
documentation_subagent.md